	   <tr><td colspan=2>Admittedly, this is a pretty sucky effect to have on a quest item, but if I happen to come across the quest pieces, I'll do the quest. Since the 49 pet, I use it on occasion. I can be found soloing the new light blue mobs at times if I'm bored, or if I'm in a truly unusual group and actually need the "tank" of my pet. If that happens, I'm obviously not in a dungeon and don't need to worry about adds, but if the puller happens to bring back more than he intended and I have to mez, reclaim energy might be a nice quick way for an enchanter to "/pet back off".... just a thought.<br>&nbsp;<br>Xxtayce E`Tiernal<br>Illusionist of Raven<br>Fennin Ro</td></tr>
